<http://example.org/tennis/tournament/Wimbledon_Championships> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "On grass, he fell to Nadal in the Queen's Club final,[82] and suffered a second-round loss at Wimbledon to Marat Safin, ending a streak of five straight major semifinals.[83]" .
