<http://example.org/tennis/player/Botic_van_de_Zandschulp> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "At the Davis Cup Finals in Málaga, Botic van de Zandschulp beat Nadal as Spain lost to the Netherlands in the quarterfinals.[377][378]" .
<http://example.org/tennis/tournament/French_Open> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "In 2019, former world No. 1 and 1995 French Open champion Thomas Muster stated: \"Rafael Nadal is the best clay-court player ever\".[426]" .
<http://example.org/tennis/player/Steffi_Graf> <http://example.org/tennis/ontology/won> <http://example.org/tennis/tournament/French_Open> .
