<http://example.org/tennis/tournament/French_Open> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "He became the third man to win every modern big title on clay (French Open, Monte-Carlo, Madrid, and Rome) after Rafael Nadal and Novak Djokovic.[197]" .
