<http://example.org/tennis/player/Nick_Kyrgios> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "He reached a record 32nd Grand Slam final after defeating Cameron Norrie in the semifinals[275] and beat Nick Kyrgios in four sets to claim his seventh Wimbledon and 21st major title, surpassing Roger Federer and moving one behind Nadal.[276][277]" .
