<http://example.org/tennis/player/Janko_Tipsarevic> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "In March, Nadal beat Janko Tipsarević and Novak Djokovic to help Spain beat Serbia in Davis Cup round one.[135][136]" .
