<http://example.org/tennis/player/Novak_Djokovic> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "Djokovic's Grand Slam debut came at the 2005 Australian Open, followed by his first Slam win at the French Open.[10]: 89–91 That year, he also reached the third round at both Wimbledon[10]: 91 and the US Open, where he beat Gaël Monfils and Mario Ančić.[46]" .
