<http://example.org/tennis/player/Roger_Federer_196> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "However, Nadal retained his No. 1 ranking during the clay-court season and won his sixth French Open title by defeating Roger Federer.[196]" .
<http://example.org/tennis/player/Annabel_Croft> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "No British man won the singles event at Wimbledon between Fred Perry in 1936 and Andy Murray in 2013, while no British woman has won since Virginia Wade in 1977, although Annabel Croft and Laura Robson won the Girls' Championship in 1984 and 2008 respectively." .
