<http://example.org/tennis/player/Rafael_Nadal> <http://example.org/tennis/provenance/evidenceText> "Nadal holds the men's all-time records for the most majors won without losing a set (4), the most match wins at a single major (112 at the French Open), and the highest match-winning percentage at clay court majors (96.6%), among many others." .
